[https://github.com/Sarcasm/irony-mode/ Irony-mode] is a minor mode that allows clang based completion for C and C++, on the fly syntax checking and more!

==Advantages==

One of the big advantages in comparison to other tools is that irony-mode has multiple ways of defining a compilation database.
The compilation database is used as a reference what rules are used concerning compilation (headers, libraries, etc.).

==Installation==

Irony is part is part of GNU ELPA (M-x list-packages).
